Class: ExportOptionsTIFF

ExportOptionsTIFF

new ExportOptionsTIFF()

Options for exporting a document as a TIFF file, used with the exportFile method. All properties are optional. When you export a document, the appropriate file extension is appended automatically. You should not include any file extension in the file specification.
Source:
